    <string name="auto_apply_hint_label">How it works</string>
    <string name="auto_apply_hint_value">Settings are saved automatically every time you change a toggle. On reboot, the app waits for Shizuku to start (up to 5 minutes) and then re-applies them without any user interaction.\n\nRequires Shizuku to auto-start after reboot: go to Developer Options → Wireless Debugging, keep it enabled (persists across reboots on Pixel), then configure Shizuku to use Wireless ADB. No root required.</string>

